{"tid":1708711,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"大家有無聽過happy corner 固定師？","createTime":"2019-11-11T16:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T16:45:10.000Z","uid":72962,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d16bdb980facd47bf6003c48eff56f073ae7fdbc","tid":1708711,"uid":72962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:11:42.000Z","msg":"細個我成日畀人欺凌<br />\n個個男仔就圍住我打<br />\n一開始我都可以好似呢個人咁走到<br />\n<br />\n落單便衣狗被鶳逃走上消防車避難<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1708452/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1708452/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/heoj9\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2Fheoj9&d=KwnMNtvToZrWMgCiTfGJQZMi8MJ45PejcSMOUziyDL0%3D&h=18396207\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/heoj9</a><br />\n<br />\n之後佢哋就慢慢發展到有專人捉住我手手腳腳<br />\n仲叫自己做固定師<br />\n只要core肌肉唔夠勁<br />\n就點都郁唔到<br />\n然後就玩happy corner 任佢哋魚肉了<br />\n<br />\nIn case 有人唔知咩係happy corner<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">眾人把被害者抬起，抓緊手腳，強制打開雙腿，並</span></span>移至柱狀物撞擊或磨擦其下體。在香港，這些行為通常稱為「corn人」、「被人corn」；在台灣則稱為「阿」（阿魯巴）與「被阿」；受臺灣流行文化影響，「阿魯巴」一詞亦在中國大陸風靡，並逐漸成為東南沿海部份地區（如福建、廣東、上海等地）對此類活動的稱呼之一。補：在大陸，實際上則有「開人」「鋸人」「a人」等稱呼，甚至還有「抗鋸從嚴」的說法，在大陸，其實這一系列行為，一般不會造成傷害，常常以被阿者的大腿根部「撞」向門框/柱子。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n畢業之後問返佢地<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">佢地就話唔洗每個都濕我一拳嘅<br />\n最緊要大家一齊恰到我<br />\n完成一致嘅目標就ok</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f4f3eecf03f0c770aa373ee27afe6456267182b2","tid":1708711,"uid":72962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:14:24.000Z","msg":"有冇人而家會咁做"},{"pid":"8d839362e7793d3d8282f9d456407501b1e5aa66","tid":1708711,"uid":72962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:15:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b7d73dc36a253c3b89c31a317e1caaf9e07e89c3","tid":1708711,"uid":274390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:19:10.000Z","msg":"想知痴屋企地板用Flex glue 好唔好用<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1708695\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1708695</a>"},{"pid":"5aa96bf787a5a2962d59181f7c3c3e1ab1c60857","tid":1708711,"uid":13173,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:35:14.000Z","msg":"記得搶埋啲軍備，唔好浪費"},{"pid":"7a5bcefabecd5f759284594c75c09ca2b37ba38a","tid":1708711,"uid":54549,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-11T16:45:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}